Quickstrike:





Quickstrike looked around. Black Arachnia was gone, and Megatron and 
Tarantsulas were left, two bots who he knew that would kill him if 
they knew about his damage. He made sure he was out of their sights. 
He transformed to beast mode and skittered off to a spot at the side 
of the cave that had a nice hidding spot. He crawled under it, with a 
layer of rock over top of it, so it was low enough that his flat body 
could fit through it. He curled around to the front and hunkered 
down.
